<h2>Priority seats</h2>
<p>All buses, Tubes, trains and trams have clearly marked priority seats for anyone who needs them. If one isn't available, ask if someone will give up a seat. </p>
<p>You can apply for a <a href="/transport-accessibility/please-offer-me-a-seat"><strong>Please Offer Me a Seat</strong></a> badge
and card or a <a href="/transport-accessibility/baby-on-board"><strong>Baby on Board</strong></a> badge to help you get a seat if you need one.</p>
</div>
